title: Bobby Shares The Crazy Thing His Therapist Asked Him To Do + Our Top TV Shows of the Decade + ‘Just the Keys, Please’ Music Game!
itunes:title: Bobby Shares The Crazy Thing His Therapist Asked Him To Do + Our Top TV Shows of the Decade + ‘Just the Keys, Please’ Music Game!
description:
Bobby talks about how his therapist asked him if he wanted to bring in his closets friends, like Amy or Eddie, to talk about some of his issues. Each member of the show gives our Top TV Show of the Decade. We play a fun music game where we have to identify the song by just the piano part!
